# Reverse proxy with automatic HTTPS in front of Dalang SSO.
# Caddy handles TLS certs (Let's Encrypt) and, in recent builds, offers a
# post-quantum hybrid key exchange (X25519MLKEM768) out of the box — see docs/PQC.md.
#
#   caddy run --config deploy/Caddyfile
#
# sso.dalang.io must resolve to this host (A + AAAA already configured).

sso.dalang.io {
	encode gzip
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8080
}
